              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Energy and width of the excited states of 6He",
                "were obtained with the spectra shape analysis by using",
                "the Breit-Wigner formula:",
                "E1=18.3+-0.2 MeV, Wid1=0.4+-0.2 MeV. This Wid1 value",
                "does not correspond to the true  width of the 18.3 MeV",
                "6He* state because its determination by the (Et, Et)",
                "spectrum is affected by the limited accessible Ett",
                "relative energy interval of about 0.7 MeV only."
              ]
            }
